					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"users",
						"{{userId}}",
						"role"
					]
				},
				"description": "Update a user's role assignment. This endpoint:\n- Removes all existing roles from the user\n- Assigns the new specified role\n- Requires Admin permissions\n- Cannot update your own role\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `roleId` (required): GUID of the role to assign\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `userId` (required): GUID of the user to update"
			},
